Download

	The latest stable version is 1.0.

* Release

	Cage releases are published to maven central. If you use maven just add this
	to your pom:

+---
<dependency>
  <groupId>com.github.cage</groupId>
  <artifactId>cage</artifactId>
  <version>1.0</version>
</dependency>
+---

	If you are not using maven you can manually download the binary, javadoc and
	source release jar files directly from the
	{{{http://repo1.maven.org/maven2/com/github/cage/cage}repository}}.

* Source

	The source code of Cage is available trough git from
	{{{https://github.com/akiraly/cage}GitHub}}.
